Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,2000)\pos(640,460)\bord0}阿蘭達斯聯合王國   國境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,630)\c&HFAFAFA&\be1}因戈爾米亞軍    東北方面前線部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友軍已經開始攻擊了 動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪大陸霸權的兩方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯聯合王國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及因戈爾米亞多國統合體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對擁有豐富資源的阿蘭達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈爾米亞在南下過程中集結多國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷增強國力軍力 步步緊逼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯方的戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於節節敗退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已收縮至國境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fsp0\bord1.5}Great Wall{\fscx600}\h\N{\r}此處 長城如銅牆鐵壁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈爾米亞的攻擊多次受挫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥眼看要進入膠著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍正不斷集結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大阿蘭達斯建國以來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長城曾無數次抵擋下蠻族入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可慌的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所言正是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我國擁有無數光輝歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕上我們來視察 不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴下面 會帶他們打贏這場苦戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 都這會了還{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的心情我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓將軍們也立刻動身前往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:01:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓他們礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的只是振奮軍心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侵略?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍爭?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是解放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵國雖豐饒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但人民生活幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案是否
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又是為何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位高權重者只知中飽私囊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剝削
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為滿足私慾挑起戰爭所致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧 諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救阿蘭達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將鄰國的國民與國土 從腐敗政權手中解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥是解放戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敢於如此下定論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這膽量值得學習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fsp0\bord1.5}Bloody Hopper{\fscx1350}\h\N{\r}躍動死神隊已成功侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部隊向正門移動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掩護不要疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞倫斯 別提前打開醬汁包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這類軍糧 要把米鋪在盤子上蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁這時間打開醬汁包正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼區別嘛 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒區別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 所以你才是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是 知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂啦 快點弄好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也好不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候更該拿出骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞倫斯先生 光琉 快點給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急什麼 老夫來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字隊長 該吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛放下行李 但要對不住他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被記恨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 獨立第八部隊放棄這一要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄大型車輛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迅速整理食物及武器彈藥等可攜帶資源
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗 還吃什麼吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我吃兩口飯怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜 有空就把這個搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新來的 準備好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分明剛剛才到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對什麼有不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,食物? 命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 這不挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說算是吃到飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有條不紊有條不紊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想幸福你也得琢磨一下品味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,品味{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 戰場上品味很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了 回頭聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲機 勞倫斯機 時宗機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備完畢立刻出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂了隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你連控制機體走路都不會?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解 時宗機會好好走路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的機師們真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且慢 將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在後方指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方部隊正等著將軍的激勵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經刻不容緩 請立刻{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上隨機應變最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們如今的使命只不過是視察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的吧 泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須返回西北方面軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘快制定出反攻計劃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳令下去 就算全軍覆沒 也要死守這座基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通電全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷落了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老頭子們在現場搗了不少亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵力本就懸殊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本打不贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到我方暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活著回到<不退之門> 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是他的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您指泉大佐?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們莫非一直在逃跑?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼回事 連這個都不知道就跟著走?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那友軍們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是待在那個偏僻地帶 本來能去營救的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜我們為什麼被安排在那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被嫌棄了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你挺聰明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是正義的夥伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算我們去了 又能幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杯水車薪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別婆婆媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們聽隊長的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟著他 我們就不會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這些事等你獨當一面後在考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能獨當一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord0\bord1.5\fsp0}TRAIL KRIEGER{\fscx1450}\h\N{\r}兩台曳戰者先導 席加負責支援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上陣了呢 新來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可怕 在生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得先擼一發放鬆放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 不愧是班長 知道得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面山谷裡沒有水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是條能走的道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前搬運物資時曾走過那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近就不知怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們出生前 那邊也是河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一切都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 行進路線上發現被毀車輛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是受到了人為襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經進因戈爾米亞的勢力範圍了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,召回曳戰者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路線保持不變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本隊暫時待機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲機 時宗機繼續前進 探明周圍狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迂回進山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別摔跤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 在學校學過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是教室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不能鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方有人開火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車輛行駛聲 正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有友方部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近未確認到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你們去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別動哦 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平民?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遭受攻擊的 是平民卡車及所屬不明的裝甲車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追擊方是因戈爾米亞軍的拖車 以及兩台曳戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在需儘早與大部隊匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能進行無謂的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個推理也成立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道要讓平民等死?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武裝的平民?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風險太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果真是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<如果>不過是個假設 不能讓戰友冒風險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令 進時宗上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皆駿先生 皆駿先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續確認周圍狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出最適路線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然不想犧牲戰友 那我去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了 這曳戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是多少來著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 快一點 吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是平民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撐住 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再堅持10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撐{\rsymbol}…{\r}撐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂 我懂是懂{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 怎麼能逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這鬧不好是要掉腦袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當兵的肯定不懂啦 大軟蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來救你的 就不能客氣點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord1.5\fsp0}Argevollen Stabilis Prima\N{\r}銀色殲滅者穩定型原型機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色{\rsymbol}…{\r}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總比被搶走強 總比被毀掉強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要駕駛它 駕駛它逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能駕駛就早駕駛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不會{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只能拼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者 裝置 喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統啟動流程 運行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈茲福特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辨識密碼 0612 0530
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新錄入 吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈茲福特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是機師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 多好的點子 我真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我駕駛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁 增援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動 然後戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是問那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動程式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該先確認哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有什麼武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動程式{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握住操縱杆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想著要做什麼 在腦中想像出實景進行操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意別胡亂嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙動起來沒有延遲 完全按照我思維在動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼沒打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,節奏太強了啊 太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是你太廢了吧 還什麼節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字隊長 那是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,500)\bord3\be1\fs60\fad(500,0)}覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:06.45,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}この高き無望の空でいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:11.07,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}その意思は膝を立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:19.83,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:22.34,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.15,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:31.90,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.39,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.27,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:47.08,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:52.22,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:57.47,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:02.04,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:03.29,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:07.67,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:14.30,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:15.85,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:23.61,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:26.35,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.27,0:22:06.45,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}總有一天 向著這無望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.45,0:22:11.07,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志將一飛沖天
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.15,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是戰友嗎{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.41,0:22:31.90,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}當走之路是黑暗嗎{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.39,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光閃動
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.27,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}無名感情在胸中翻湧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.46,0:22:47.08,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此時此刻在此地 尚不能結束-
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.08,0:22:52.22,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那麼就做好活下去的準備吧
